11(7): E060706.5 (<http://www.eurosurveillance.org/ew/2006/060706.asp#5>)
4. Noel JS, Fankhauser RL, Ando T, Monroe SS, Glass RI. Identification of a
distinct strain of "Norwalk-like Viruses" having a global distribution. J
Infect Dis 1999; 179(6): 1334-44.
5. Takkinen J. Recent norovirus outbreaks on river and seagoing cruise
